{"title":"Weapons","content":"Weapons are items that player characters use to inflict damage in combat. They may be obtained as a reward from quests, as a drop from monsters or crafted through various professions.\n\nWeapons deal Impact damage, which is primarily determined by the weapon's Strength attribute. Certain weapon types, however, have a chance to inflict alternative damage types based on their specific characteristics. The speed at which weapons attack is also determined by the weapon's type. One-handed weaponry can be used alongside a shield.\n\nMuch like other equipment, weapons come in four tiers of rarity: Common, Uncommon, Rare and Epic.\n\nWeaponry with the Guard's prefix can be worn regardless of player faction. They can be obtained from monster drops and quests in Hopeport and Hopeforest prior to choosing a faction.\n\nCryoknight weaponry, Guardian  weaponry and Hammermage  weaponry can be created through the Blacksmith, Bonewright and Stonemason professions respectively.\n\n","tables":[[{"Weapon":{"text":"Guard's Kanabo","links":[{"type":"internal","page":"Guard's Kanabo"}]},"Faction":{"text":"N/A"},"Element":{"text":"Tempestae (Tempestae_damage icon.png)","links":[{"type":"internal","page":"Tempestae"}]},"Range":{"text":"Melee"},"1H/2H":{"text":"1H 1-Hand icon.png","formatting":{"bold":["1-Hand icon.png"]}},"Attack Speed":{"text":""}},{"Weapon":{"text":"Guard's Sword","links":[{"type":"internal","page":"Guard's Sword"}]},"Faction":{"text":"N/A"},"Element":{"text":"N/A"},"Range":{"text":"Melee"},"1H/2H":{"text":"1H 1-Hand icon.png","formatting":{"bold":["1-Hand icon.png"]}},"Attack Speed":{"text":""}},{"Weapon":{"text":"Guard's Halberd","links":[{"type":"internal","page":"Guard's Halberd"}]},"Faction":{"text":"N/A"},"Element":{"text":"Cryonae (Cryonae_damage icon.png)","links":[{"type":"internal","page":"Cryonae"}]},"Range":{"text":"Melee"},"1H/2H":{"text":"2H 2-Hand icon.png","formatting":{"bold":["2-Hand icon.png"]}},"Attack Speed":{"text":""}},